nodes.text: The Tee were a species of scalefish native to the planet Naboo. They lived alongside six other scalefish species in the waters around the city Otoh Gunga in Lake Paonga, and could also be found in Abyss, where they were preyed upon indiscriminately by colo claw fish and opee sea killers that dwelt there. Tiny yobshrimp lived in the gills of tee, and they were licked out and eaten by laa scalefish.
